description:
The feeding of the 5,000 is a miracle that is so famous, it is referenced in society, even within non-religious communities. Faced with the seemingly impossible task of feeding thousands of people with such little supplies, Jesus performed a miracle of duplication to the extent that there wer even leftovers at the end! Even during difficult times, Jesus had a way out that nobody else could comprehend.
